OL,6,FThe position was scrapped in 2022 and
OL,7,Fthere have been several unsuccessful
OL,8,Fattempts to reintroduce it until
OL,9,FDeputy Elaine Millar's proposition
OL,10,Fpassed by 25 votes to 20 with one
OL,11,Fabstention and one uncounted vote that
OL,12,Fwas cast too late.
OL,14,FThe minister believes the current
OL,15,FAssembly "has lacked the perspective
OL,16,Fand overview that comes from having
OL,17,Fmembers who are elected on behalf of
OL,18,Fthe whole island".
