OL,6,F"I think it's wrong to assume that
OL,7,Fpeople don't vote because of the
OL,8,Fabolition of senators, I think people
OL,9,Fdon't vote because they don't have
OL,10,Fconfidence in the system which is
OL,11,Fstill complicated.
OL,13,F"What would help is if we had a single
OL,14,Fclass of States member which served
OL,15,Ffor the same period of time."
OL,17,FA referendum on electoral reform held
OL,18,Fin 2013 saw the option that included
OL,19,Fsenators receive the fewest votes.
